[Косвенная речь] Перескажите просьбу или приказ в косвенной речи.

1) Mother (to me): “Clean the room!”
Mother told me _______________

2) Nelly: “Help my sister!”
Nelly asked ____________

3) Fred: “Wash your hands!”
Fred told me _____________

4) Anna: “Open the window, please.”
Anna asked me _______________

5) Tom: “Don’t be late!”
Tom demanded___________

6) Jane: “Can you turn down the music?”
Jane asked me _____________

to clean the room, to help her sister, to wash my hands, 
to open the window, not to be late, to turn down the music.

