[Косвенная речь] Перескажите вопросы в косвенной речи.

1) Bella: “When did you return?”
Bella wanted to know ______________.

2) Christopher (to me): “Do you want to dance tonight?”
Christopher asked me ______________.

3) Mark: “Has John read this book?”
Mark asked ________________.

4) Ronald (to me): “Where does Maria live?”
Ronald asked me _____________.

5) Andrew: “Will Shawn have lunch with us?”
Andrew asked___________________.

6) Justin: “What are you doing?”
Justin asked me _______________.

7) Anne: “Must I do the shopping today?”
Anne wanted to know________________.

when I had returned, if I wanted to dance that night, if John had read that book, where Marial lived, 
if Shawn would have lunch with us, what I was doing, if she must do the shopping that day.

